## ⚙️ CONFIG.YAML

```yaml
grid:
  symbol: "BTC/USDT"
  price_min: 80000
  price_max: 90000
  num_levels: 5
  total_capital_usdt: 10.0
  max_order_usdt: 2.0

risk:
  max_daily_loss_usdt: 2.0
  max_open_orders: 10
  min_order_usdt: 0.5

loop:
  interval_seconds: 30
  max_consecutive_errors: 5
```

